    .t-max-w-l.t-mx-auto.t-text-center(class="t-w-4/5 t-px-lg sm:t-w-auto")
      br
      h2.t-text-lg(class="md:t-text-2xl t-pb-md").
        “Rent the Runway has been a go-to for all things fashion since its inception
        <br/>
